                     Bureau of Transportation Statistics

             Motor Carrier Financial and Operational Statistics
     __________________________________________________________________

   The Motor Carrier Financial Statistics Program conducts annual and
   quarterly data collections of motor carriers of property and
   passengers. The program collects industry financial, employee,
   operating, and other data.  Detailed Description
